      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'The company monitors and interfaces with all things occult. Keeping the
    old ones at bay since ''86!

    You have a desk job here and you boss tasks
    you with preventing the re-emergence of a being beyond our comprehension, older
    than the universe and blah blah.

    Sacrifices must be made on a routine basis.
    The sanguine blood of the mortal toil must ever flow into its open maw. Basically
    you have to press this button every 15 seconds.

    If you miss too much time
    it will emerge, not only will it be the death of all and the end of times. But
    you will be fired.

'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 1e057b34cac5b4a4288076aa5ae86a46, type: 2}
